casebody.data:
No. 120,

Misc.

Sheffield v. Eyman, Warden, et al. Petitioner pro se. Robert W. Pickrell, former Attorney General of Arizona, Darrell F. Smith, Attorney General, William E. Eubank, Chief Assistant Attorney General, and Sidney M. Rosen and Robert S. Murlless, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondents.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as a petition for writ of certiorari, certiorari is denied.
